FINDINGS: Lungs/Pleura: Similar degree and distribution of the multifocal airspace opacities in both lungs. No pleural effusion. No pneumothorax. IMPRESSION: Similar appearance of the multifocal airspace disease. Support hardware are located in standard positions, as described above.
